BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:odyzpzThKVJflb2_LxxFm
SUMMARY:Unexpected Productions: Seattle Theatresports Improv
DTSTAMP:20260405T040254Z
DTSTART:20260405T043000Z
DESCRIPTION:Fridays & Saturdays from 9:30pm - 11pm Seattle’s high-energy im
	prov battle where your suggestions shape every scene. Fast\, funny\, unpre
	dictable comedy Fri. & Sat. 9:30 Welcome to Seattle’s funnest improv comed
	y show\, a high-energy\, no-rules showdown where your ideas shape every sc
	ene. Seattle Theatresports at Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater in Pi
	ke Place Market is part comedy battle\, part game night\, and completely p
	owered by the crowd. Boo the judges. Cheer the Gum Wall race and laugh til
	 it hurts! Every show\, two teams of top Seattle improvisers go head to he
	ad\, performing games\, stories\, characters\, and scenes inspired entirel
	y by your suggestions. Judges score the rounds\, decide the winners\, and 
	shape the fun (as we boo them). No scripts. No safety nets. Just fast thin
	king\, bold choices\, and pure creative mayhem. This isn’t your parents’ i
	mprov show\, unless your parents were super cool. Buy Tickets\n\nhttps://w
	ww.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/seattle-theatresports-improv/?occur
	rence=2026-04-04
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/seattle-theatresports-i
	mprov/?occurrence=2026-04-04
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H30M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:j2X4UzuuUHX65w-fHi1F1
SUMMARY:The Original Food and Culture Tour of Pike Place Market
DTSTAMP:20260405T040254Z
DTSTART:20260405T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:VOTED 10 BEST FOOD TOURS IN THE COUNTRY BY USA TODAY! Join Savo
	r Seattle for Seattle’s original food and cultural tour of Pike Place Mark
	et! On their signature tour\, they will take you on a journey through the 
	lively and bustling days in the heart of Seattle: Pike Place Market. While
	 their guides give you the most delicious tastings at eight different part
	ners. You’ll also learn the history of the Market and hear the stories of 
	the small-batch food and craft producers that make this place one of Seatt
	le’s most beloved landmarks. Find out why fish fly\, why a pig is our masc
	ot\, how the “Original” Starbucks was founded\, how an alleyway became cov
	ered in gum\, what made Pike Place Market one of Anthony Bourdain’s favori
	te places\, and many more pieces of info Seattle Savor guides we’ll be thr
	illed to share with you while you savor culinary offerings. Once you’re do
	ne\, you’ll be equipped and ready to dive deeper into the historic neighbo
	rhood. Tours are available daily\, starting at 10am and 2\n\nhttps://www.p
	ikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/the-original-food-and-culture-tour-of-p
	ike-place-market/?occurrence=2026-04-05
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/the-original-food-and-c
	ulture-tour-of-pike-place-market/?occurrence=2026-04-05
LOCATION:Pike Place Market
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:7xIjjUbBic0Te8_e-eztS
SUMMARY:The Production: An Improvised Mockumentary
DTSTAMP:20260405T040254Z
DTSTART:20260406T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Sundays at 7pm Every week\, a brand-new workplace. A fresh batc
	h of quirky coworkers. And—worst of all—a different boss. Step inside the 
	chaos of an unpredictable workday as the Unexpected Productions cast impro
	vises an all-new\, on-the-spot mockumentary. From the office know-it-all t
	o the slacker skating by\, you'll meet the characters you love to hate—and
	 hate to admit you recognize. No script\, no second takes—just pure\, unsc
	ripted workplace mayhem. Buy Tickets\n\nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/12560
	66301119?aff=oddtdtcreator
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/1256066301119?aff=oddtdtcreator
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:xAwPcifatdfn1Spv_FhGh
SUMMARY:Improv Happy Hour
DTSTAMP:20260405T040254Z
DTSTART:20260405T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Improv Happy Hour—where comedy is unscripted\, unpr
	edictable\, and unbelievably fun! From movie mashups to literary spoofs an
	d bold\, experimental comedy\, our quick-thinking performers turn your sug
	gestions into hilarious scenes on the spot. This family-friendly show at t
	he iconic Gum Wall in Pike Place Market guarantees a night of laughter\, s
	urprises\, and improv magic you won’t forget. Bring your wildest ideas\, y
	our loudest laughs\, and get ready for a one-of-a-kind comedy experience—b
	ecause at Improv Happy Hour\, anything can happen (and usually does)! Buy 
	Tickets\n\nhttps://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/improv-happy-ho
	ur-2/?occurrence=2026-04-05
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/improv-happy-hour-2/?oc
	currence=2026-04-05
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:HA6qExMH0SXwmw00_kBrm
SUMMARY:No Strings Attached: An Improvised Puppet Show for Grownups
DTSTAMP:20260405T040254Z
DTSTART:20260406T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Sundays at 7pm At Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater \, pup
	pets let their hair down (or strings loose) in No Strings Attached —a hila
	rious\, adults improv puppet show. After a long day entertaining the kids\
	, these puppets are ready to play—singing bawdy songs\, cracking jokes\, a
	nd getting up to all kinds of outrageous fun. And the best part? You call 
	the shots with your suggestions! Don’t miss this one-of-a-kind comedy show
	 at Pike Place Market. It’s puppets\, it’s improv\, and it’s guaranteed to
	 make you laugh. THIS SHOW CONTAINS MATURE CONTENT\, LANGUAGE\, AND SITUAT
	IONS Buy Tickets\n\nhttps://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/no-str
	ings-attached-an-improvised-puppet-show-for-grownups-3/?occurrence=2026-04
	-05
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/no-strings-attached-an-
	improvised-puppet-show-for-grownups-3/?occurrence=2026-04-05
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:B3SZZADbN3wCbRIiQpCWg
SUMMARY:THIS IS FOR YOU: An Improvised Theatre Poetry Experience
DTSTAMP:20260405T040254Z
DTSTART:20260405T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Step into a world where your memories spark the unexpected\, yo
	ur objects tell untold stories\, and your life becomes art in motion. With
	 a swirl of spontaneous theater\, hand-typed poetry\, and the soulful soun
	ds of live musicians on stage each night unfolds like a dream—unrepeatable
	\, electric\, and uniquely yours. One moment\, you're laughing at a scene 
	born from a trinket in your pocket\; the next\, a poem crafted just for yo
	u finds its way into your hands. This is poetry in motion. This is music i
	n the moment. This is theater made from the fabric of your life. Come laug
	h. Come cry. Come as you are. ✨ THIS IS FOR YOU! ✨ Don’t miss this once-in
	-a-lifetime fusion of words\, sound\, and improvisation. April is the mont
	h of poetry—come celebrate the magic! Get Tickets\n\nhttps://www.pikeplace
	market.org/events-calendar/this-is-for-you-an-improvised-theatre-poetry-ex
	perience/?occurrence=2026-04-05
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/this-is-for-you-an-impr
	ovised-theatre-poetry-experience/?occurrence=2026-04-05
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
